The paper discusses hyperparameter optimization in deep learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since the paper specifically focuses on deep learning, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.AI and cs.CV. The other two sub-categories, cs.NE and cs.SY, are less likely but still possible since they also deal with optimization problems.
